André Alerme https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andr%C3%A9_Alerme 0 André Alerme (9 September 1877 – 2 February 1960) was a French actor. Alerme was born Marie André Alerme in Dieppe, Seine-Maritime, France and died at the age of 82 in Montrichard, Loir-et-Cher, France.
